    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/383dc6ebaa38abf00226798082a66e09.avif?t=1729022533\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><strong>逻辑与组织拼图</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/4b9c844210527bc4a3c1ec92dacfec97.poster.avif?t=1729022533\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/4b9c844210527bc4a3c1ec92dacfec97.webm?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/4b9c844210527bc4a3c1ec92dacfec97.mp4?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>经过多年的战斗，一群维京人决定是时候征服新的土地了。 在Njord神的保护下，一个专门从事航海的新氏族开始寻找荣耀！</strong><br><br><strong>Dolmenjord</strong> 是一款受北欧神话启发的游戏，维京人需要帮助来组织他们的建筑物和村庄，从而解决难题并统治新大陆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/f51a800a2d9c8834de99abb7fc829fc9.avif?t=1729022533\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><strong>游戏玩法</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1b9509fb1e67395bdf50a45290d22c64.poster.avif?t=1729022533\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1b9509fb1e67395bdf50a45290d22c64.webm?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1b9509fb1e67395bdf50a45290d22c64.mp4?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>按照规则设置每个村庄：<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1bdfb24f36e1cf1dae5dde3bccb1224f.webp?t=1729022533\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 放置所有可用的房屋和行道块。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1bdfb24f36e1cf1dae5dde3bccb1224f.webp?t=1729022533\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 每个房屋必须面向行道。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1bdfb24f36e1cf1dae5dde3bccb1224f.webp?t=1729022533\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 完整的行道必须通向港口。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/07d4ef123a7f1b629e0ac7a34a8308a2.avif?t=1729022533\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><strong>特征</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1bdfb24f36e1cf1dae5dde3bccb1224f.webp?t=1729022533\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 北欧文化典型的轻松氛围和效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1bdfb24f36e1cf1dae5dde3bccb1224f.webp?t=1729022533\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 非常适合只想放松的北欧文化爱好者。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1bdfb24f36e1cf1dae5dde3bccb1224f.webp?t=1729022533\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 60 个关卡为您带来乐趣和大脑刺激。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/1bdfb24f36e1cf1dae5dde3bccb1224f.webp?t=1729022533\" width=20 height=20 /></span>  04 不同的气候。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/34c1bd8832246397a512bd77bbc775a4.poster.avif?t=1729022533\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/34c1bd8832246397a512bd77bbc775a4.webm?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/34c1bd8832246397a512bd77bbc775a4.mp4?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/8a9a56a6b7013531ecb8b14ad2b29af0.poster.avif?t=1729022533\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/8a9a56a6b7013531ecb8b14ad2b29af0.webm?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/8a9a56a6b7013531ecb8b14ad2b29af0.mp4?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>早期岛屿的谜题很简单，但随着探索的推进，谜题变得越来越具有挑战性。 如果您喜欢更轻松的旅程，那很好！<br>您可以随时在选项菜单中启用<strong>休闲模式</strong>。 提示按钮将可用。 单击后，它会显示人行道的建议形状。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/3fcfa922a83e086c1590fd86e846f36d.poster.avif?t=1729022533\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/3fcfa922a83e086c1590fd86e846f36d.webm?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/3fcfa922a83e086c1590fd86e846f36d.mp4?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/04d767c9b2614e3eb112f96384ffb05a.poster.avif?t=1729022533\" width=346 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/04d767c9b2614e3eb112f96384ffb05a.webm?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899950/extras/04d767c9b2614e3eb112f96384ffb05a.mp4?t=1729022533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>添加到您的愿望清单并关注游戏！",
